   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Digital Impact Alliance</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1) Developing open sourced digital solutions that can be readily and widely used by the development community; 2) developing and trialing new business and replicable private-public partnership models to scale-up cost-effective digital programmes; 3) improving policy-makers understanding of complex digital policy issues; and 4) improving development community skills and capabilities in investing and adopting digital technologies to support programs.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This programme will serve as a strategic vehicle for delivering on DFID&#x2019;s Digital Strategy 2018-2020, which aims to harness digital technology to tackle global poverty and deliver on the SDGs</narrative>
